OL,3,CSadiq Khan gives Oxford Street
OL,4,Cpedestrianisation greenlight
OL,6,FThe Mayor has given the go ahead for
OL,7,Fthe controversial plan to
OL,8,Fpedestrianise Oxford Street.
OL,10,FIt means vehicles will be prohibited
OL,11,Ffrom accessing a 0.7-mile stretch
OL,12,Fbetween Oxford Circus and Marble Arch.
OL,14,FSir Sadiq said: "I am delighted to be
OL,15,Fmoving forward with my bold vision to
OL,16,Ftransform Oxford Street into a world-
OL,17,Fleading urban space for shopping,
OL,18,Fleisure and outdoor events.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
