PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772118239
OL,3,CSadiq Khan gives Oxford Street
OL,4,Cpedestrianisation greenlight
OL,6,F"Following TfL's detailed
OL,7,Fconsultation, I've today made the
OL,8,Fdecision to move ahead with these
OL,9,Fexciting changes to the nation's high
OL,10,Fstreet. We will outline more details
OL,11,Fin the coming days, as we continue
OL,12,Fbuilding a better more prosperous
OL,13,FLondon for everyone."
OL,15,FIt comes after Transport for London
OL,16,Fpublished the findings of an eight-
OL,17,Fweek public consultation into the
OL,18,Fplans. It said after considering the
OL,19,Ffeedback, no changes are being
OL,20,Fsuggested to the scheme.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@UO]
