PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772118239
OL,3,CSadiq Khan gives Oxford Street
OL,4,Cpedestrianisation greenlight
OL,6,FThe plans would close the stretch of
OL,7,Froad between Great Portland Street and
OL,8,FOrchard Street to private motorised
OL,9,Fvehicles, buses, taxis and private
OL,10,Fhire vehicles, cycles, scooters and
OL,11,Fpedicabs.
OL,13,FTfL says emergency services would
OL,14,Fstill have access to the street at any
OL,15,Ftime, and that servicing vehicles
OL,16,Fcould access the traffic-free area
OL,17,Ffrom midnight to 07:00 to support
OL,18,Flocal businesses and retailers.
