OL,3,CSadiq Khan gives Oxford Street
OL,4,Cpedestrianisation greenlight
OL,6,FWorks to pedestrianise the road are
OL,7,Fexpected to start in the summer, with
OL,8,Fthe first traffic-free section
OL,9,Fintroduced by the end of the year.
